{"tid":2074972,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【業績速報】壹傳媒去年度虧損擴大至4.2億 線上訂閱收入2.8億","createTime":"2020-06-22T13:29:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T15:21:49.000Z","uid":33028,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a5b4b61026e7cc265075ae3d82b13ca8b67bff2e","tid":2074972,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T13:29:44.000Z","msg":"壹傳媒（282）公佈截至3月底止去年度業績，收入按年跌11%，至11.58億元，虧損較去年擴大至4.15億元，每股基本虧損15.8仙。<br />\n<br />\n當中，去年9月才展開的標準定價線上訂閱業務，錄得收入2.77億元。互聯網廣告收入、內容供應及開發手機遊戲及應用程式收入2.69億元，按年跌53%。報章銷售為3.17億元，升4.6%；報章廣告收入為1.63億元，跌32%。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200622/56PKXSTQF6GK4JTNOHIVHZO4CY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200622%2F56PKXSTQF6GK4JTNOHIVHZO4CY%2F&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F8txnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=1ba588e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200622%2F56PKXSTQF6GK4JTNOHIVHZO4CY%2F&h=cf9495df\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200622/56PKXSTQF6GK4JTNOHIVHZO4CY/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www1.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/sehk/2020/0622/2020062201037_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.hkexnews.hk%2Flistedco%2Flistconews%2Fsehk%2F2020%2F0622%2F2020062201037_c.pdf&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F8txnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=633c15cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www1.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/sehk/2020/0622/2020062201037_c.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"7141ce976e585f9d98228b0a2d4872d81c63fa33","tid":2074972,"uid":132587,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T13:31:59.000Z","msg":"訂閱有成2m已經好多<br />\n真係要諗諗計點止蝕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14dfc61226d78592c8f70ea9e7e4a82144e0b9af","tid":2074972,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7141ce976e585f9d98228b0a2d4872d81c63fa33","tid":2074972,"uid":132587,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"cite